    <p>Learn more about our services and specialties:</p>

    <div class="specialties-box">
        <div class="specialty-item">Internal Medicine</div>
        <div class="specialty-item">Pediatrics</div>
        <div class="specialty-item">Surgery</div>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-4 text-muted">If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
